{"tid":2233882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李居明大師又有大戲新作《共和三夢》","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T13:20:53.000Z","uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"363edff3099e41632976adbbeee2fa03beab12d7","tid":2233882,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"大師又有新作《共和三夢》，今次終於入戲曲中心做，可能因為驚新光唔夠位（加而家要隔開坐）<br />\n龍貫天繼續做老毛同Trump<br />\n呂珊做川島芳子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120903058_3260744587377559_4273271722546202497_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=ZmTYkoKbTsQAX-e62mO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=67da1409ee948dd3fcc3e9fb6140e8ac&amp;oe=5FA41AF3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120903058_3260744587377559_4273271722546202497_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DZmTYkoKbTsQAX-e62mO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D67da1409ee948dd3fcc3e9fb6140e8ac%26oe%3D5FA41AF3&h=2509273a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新光中國戲曲文化 呈獻 李居明振興粵劇第35個新戲寶<br />\n劇目: 虛雲三夢第3部曲《共和三夢》<br />\n.<br />\n演員：龍貫天, 陳咏儀, 陳鴻進, 新劍郎, 鄧美玲, 王超群, 呂洪廣, 溫玉瑜, 康華, 一点鴻, 呂珊(特別情商演出)<br />\n.<br />\n演出地點: 西九文化區- 戲曲中心大劇院<br />\n演出日期: 2020年12月9-14日 (6天6場)<br />\n演出時間: 晚上7時30分<br />\n票價: $500* $400 $320 $240 $180 (*$500不設半價優惠)<br />\n.<br />\n☆虛雲三夢第3部曲，推動中國近代史教育，鼓勵與家人一起欣賞!☆<br />\n.<br />\n「新光中國會」嘅會員，可以搵細編幫你預訂靚位呀!!🤗<br />\n😗隨時Whatsapp(6338 3281)俾細編啦✌🏻<br />\n.<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n公 開 售 票： 2020年10月20 (星期二)<br />\n售 票 地 點： 戲曲中心票務處、翌日起於通利琴行(奧海城/沙田/元朗分店)發售<br />\n購 票 熱 線： 2200 0022<br />\n網 上 購 票： <a href=\"http://www.westkowloon.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.westkowloon.hk&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=19667ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.westkowloon.hk</a><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n☎️如有任何查詢，請致電2856 0161 / 6338 3281與本會職員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sunbeam.chinese.club/photos/a.353057718146275/3260744584044226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsunbeam.chinese.club%2Fphotos%2Fa.353057718146275%2F3260744584044226&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=9c0dacd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sunbeam.chinese.club/photos/a.353057718146275/3260744584044226</a>"},{"pid":"77d8a0cd129b81acfaf7a86ae33fe483af7f045f","tid":2233882,"uid":49392,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"有無我要殺死丁力個仆街呢句對白先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658a3103913d4fcd0f2fb1dc1ef44264e2d84642","tid":2233882,"uid":370061,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我睇咗啲乜撚野"},{"pid":"aab163ed434c582b7ce0701ef4b5b85259bb09c8","tid":2233882,"uid":2054,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RA545Hy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA545Hy.jpg&h=bf76e894&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"032fe2ed041292769f29024f8510a8a360744c18","tid":2233882,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"扮埋龍珠擋武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"d565e4de41044e25cc8996f2025c2ae19c478a47","tid":2233882,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKVJQ1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKVJQ1x.jpg&h=6bfcbaff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cec423462b61001427040547b9d57ccf705d89e2","tid":2233882,"uid":134438